    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Machinicide is a boomer shooter with imm sim and bullet hell elements. Reduce all evil robots to scraps with a huge arsenal of futuristic weapons and  abilities, such as telekinesis, changing of gravity and many more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897010/extras/1832471abcc8565d66eb4472abbd495f.avif?t=1739815231\" width=600 height=70 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897010/extras/f2cb8887be6ba91ca3928ca6d04eee2f.avif?t=1739815231\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897010/extras_big/f2cb8887be6ba91ca3928ca6d04eee2f.avif?t=1739815231 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shock the hell out of evil bots. Use telekinesis to throw robots at other robots. Change gravity. And lots more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897010/extras/e040c7014a41a3a49eac8bc6ebb3f4f1.avif?t=1739815231\" width=600 height=70 /></span>Running out of weapons to shoot? Just point your hand at enemies to turn them into more weapons while enjoying a shower of confetti.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897010/extras/34362b6e49c015edc476140555096c39.avif?t=1739815231\" width=600 height=70 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Obliterate bosses that try to overwhelm you with large amounts of projectiles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897010/extras/0153c966903f54588c7315d6f6bfdf81.avif?t=1739815231\" width=600 height=70 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Who needs to reload when you have a near-endless supply of guns at your disposal? Just throw away your used weapons right in the face of your enemies</p>",
